    {
      "id": "s3-60",
      "sectionId": "s3",
      "title": "模式匹配",
      "body": ">\n> 模式匹配是 Elixir 很强大的特性，它允许我们匹配简单值、数据结构、甚至函数。\n>"
    },
    {
      "id": "s3-61",
      "sectionId": "s3",
      "title": "%E5%8C%B9%E9%85%8D%E5%85%83%E7%BB%84",
      "body": "%60%60%60elixir%0Aiex%3E%20%7Ba%2C%20b%2C%20c%7D%20%3D%20%7B%3Ahello%2C%20%22world%22%2C%2042%7D%0A%7B%3Ahello%2C%20%22world%22%2C%2042%7D%0Aiex%3E%20a%0A%3Ahello%0Aiex%3E%20b%0A%22world%22%0A%60%60%60",
      "encoded": true
    },
    {
      "id": "s3-62",
      "sectionId": "s3",
      "title": "匹配列表",
      "body": "```\niex> [a, b, c] = [1, 2, 3]\n[1, 2, 3]\niex> a\n1\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "s3-63",
      "sectionId": "s3",
      "title": "匹配列表的头部元素",
      "body": "```\niex> [head | tail] = [1, 2, 3]\n[1, 2, 3]\niex> head\n1\niex> tail\n[2, 3]\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "s3-64",
      "sectionId": "s3",
      "title": "Pin 操作符",
      "body": "pin 操作符，就是用已经绑定的值去匹配，而不是重新绑定一个新值。\n\n```elixir\niex> {x, ^x} = {2, 1}\n{2, 1}\niex> x\n2\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "s3-66",
      "sectionId": "s3",
      "title": "使用下划线 `_` 忽略匹配的值",
      "body": "```elixir\niex> [head | _] = [1, 2, 3]\n[1, 2, 3]\niex> head\n1\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "s4-67",
      "sectionId": "s4",
      "title": "if/else/end",
      "body": "```elixir\nif condition do\n  # 条件成立时执行的代码\nelse\n  # 条件不成立时执行的代码\nend\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "s4-68",
      "sectionId": "s4",
      "title": "case/end",
      "body": "```elixir\ncase expression do\n  pattern1 -> # 匹配 pattern1 时执行的代码\n  pattern2 -> # 匹配 pattern2 时执行的代码\n  _ -> # 其他情况执行的代码\nend\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "s4-69",
      "sectionId": "s4",
      "title": "cond/end",
      "body": "```elixir\ncond do\n  condition1 -> # 条件1成立时执行的代码\n  condition2 -> # 条件2成立时执行的代码\n  true -> # 如果没有任何条件成立，执行这里的代码\nend\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "s4-70",
      "sectionId": "s4",
      "title": "unless/do/end",
      "body": "```elixir\nunless condition do\n  # 条件为假时执行的代码\nend\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "s4-71",
      "sectionId": "s4",
      "title": "try/rescue/end",
      "body": "```elixir\ntry do\n  # 可能会引发异常的代码\nrescue\n  pattern1 -> # 匹配 pattern1 的异常处理代码\n  pattern2 -> # 匹配 pattern2 的异常处理代码\n  _ -> # 其他异常处理代码\nend\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "s4-72",
      "sectionId": "s4",
      "title": "case",
      "body": "%E5%85%81%E8%AE%B8%E5%B0%86%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%80%BC%E4%B8%8E%E8%AE%B8%E5%A4%9A%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E6%AF%94%E8%BE%83%EF%BC%8C%E7%9B%B4%E5%88%B0%E6%89%BE%E5%88%B0%E5%8C%B9%E9%85%8D%E7%9A%84%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F%EF%BC%9A%0A%0A%60%60%60elixir%0Aiex%3E%20case%20%7B1%2C%202%2C%203%7D%20do%0A%20%20%7B4%2C%205%2C%206%7D%20-%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%22This%20clause%20won't%20match%22%0A%20%20%7B1%2C%20x%2C%203%7D%20-%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%22%E8%AF%A5%E5%AD%90%E5%8F%A5%E5%B0%86%E5%8C%B9%E9%85%8D%E5%B9%B6%E7%BB%91%E5%AE%9A%20x%20%E5%88%B0%E8%AF%A5%E5%AD%90%E5%8F%A5%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%202%22%0A%20%20_%20-%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%22This%20clause%20would%20match%20any%20value%22%0Aend%0A%22%E8%AF%A5%E5%AD%90%E5%8F%A5%E5%B0%86%E5%8C%B9%E9%85%8D%E5%B9%B6%E7%BB%91%E5%AE%9A%20x%20%E5%88%B0%E8%AF%A5%E5%AD%90%E5%8F%A5%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%202%22%0A%60%60%60%0A%0A%E8%BF%98%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8when%E6%8C%87%E5%AE%9A%E9%A2%9D%E5%A4%96%E7%9A%84%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%0A%0A%60%60%60elixir%0Aiex%3E%20case%20%7B1%2C%202%2C%203%7D%20do%0A%20%20%7B1%2C%20x%2C%203%7D%20when%20x%20%3E%200%20-%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%22Will%20match%22%0A%20%20_%20-%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%22%E5%A6%82%E6%9E%9C%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%A1%E8%B6%B3%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%86%E5%8C%B9%E9%85%8D%22%0Aend%0A%22Will%20match%22%0A%60%60%60",
      "encoded": true
    },
    {
      "id": "s4-76",
      "sectionId": "s4",
      "title": "cond",
      "body": "%E5%BD%93%E6%88%91%E4%BB%AC%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E5%8C%B9%E9%85%8D%E8%80%8C%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF%E5%80%BC%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%E7%B1%BB%E4%BC%BC%E4%BA%8E%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E8%AF%AD%E8%A8%80%E7%9A%84%20%60else%20if%60%20%E6%88%96%20%60elsif%60%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%20%60cond%60%20%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E3%80%82%0A%0A%60%60%60elixir%0Aiex%3E%20cond%20do%0A%20%202%20%2B%202%20%3D%3D%205%20-%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%22This%20will%20not%20be%20true%22%0A%20%202%20*%202%20%3D%3D%203%20-%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%22Nor%20this%22%0A%20%201%20%2B%201%20%3D%3D%202%20-%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%22But%20this%20will%22%0Aend%0A%22But%20this%20will%22%0A%60%60%60%0A%0A%E5%A6%82%E6%9E%9C%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89%E7%9A%84%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E9%83%BD%E8%BF%94%E5%9B%9E%20%60nil%60%20%E6%88%96%20%60false%60%EF%BC%8C%E5%88%99%E4%BC%9A%E5%BC%95%E5%8F%91%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E9%94%99%E8%AF%AF%EF%BC%88CondClauseError%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%E5%9B%A0%E6%AD%A4%EF%BC%8C%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%20%60final%60%20%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%EF%BC%8C%E7%AD%89%E4%BA%8E%20%60true%60%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%83%E5%B0%86%E5%A7%8B%E7%BB%88%E5%8C%B9%E9%85%8D%EF%BC%9A%0A%0A%60%60%60elixir%0Aiex%3E%20cond%20do%0A%20%202%20%2B%202%20%3D%3D%205%20-%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%22This%20is%20never%20true%22%0A%20%202%20*%202%20%3D%3D%203%20-%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%22Nor%20this%22%0A%20%20true%20-%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%22%E8%BF%99%E5%A7%8B%E7%BB%88%E4%B8%BA%E7%9C%9F%EF%BC%88%E7%AD%89%E5%90%8C%E4%BA%8E%20else%EF%BC%89%22%0Aend%0A%22%E8%BF%99%E5%A7%8B%E7%BB%88%E4%B8%BA%E7%9C%9F%EF%BC%88%E7%AD%89%E5%90%8C%E4%BA%8E%20else%EF%BC%89%22%0A%60%60%60",
      "encoded": true
    },
    {
      "id": "s4-80",
      "sectionId": "s4",
      "title": "变量的作用域",
      "body": "如果在if、case和类似的构造中声明或更改了任何变量，则声明和更改将只在构造中可见。\n\n```elixir\niex> x = 1\n1\nif true do\n  x = x + 1\nend\n2\niex> x\n1\n```\n\n如果要更改值，则必须从if返回值：\n\n```elixir\niex> x = 1\n1\niex> x = if true do\n  x + 1\nelse\n  x\nend\n2\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-84",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "函数定义",
      "body": "```elixir\ndef function_name(param1, param2) do\n  # 函数体\nend\n```\n\n示例：\n\n```elixir\ndef sum(a, b) do\n  a + b\nend\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-87",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F%E5%8C%B9%E9%85%8D%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%9A%E4%B8%AA%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89",
      "body": "%60%60%60elixir%0Adef%20fun_name(%3Aatom)%20do%0A%20%20%23%20%E5%AF%B9%E4%BA%8E%20%3Aatom%20%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%0Aend%0A%0Adef%20fun_name(%22string%22)%20do%0A%20%20%23%20%E5%AF%B9%E4%BA%8E%20%22string%22%20%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%0Aend%0A%0Adef%20fun_name(number)%20when%20is_integer(number)%20do%0A%20%20%23%20%E5%AF%B9%E4%BA%8E%E6%95%B4%E6%95%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%0Aend%0A%60%60%60%0A%0A%E7%A4%BA%E4%BE%8B%EF%BC%9A%0A%0A%60%60%60elixir%0Adef%20is_positive(number)%20when%20number%20%3E%200%20do%0A%20%20true%0Aend%0A%0Adef%20is_positive(_)%2C%20do%3A%20false%0A%60%60%60",
      "encoded": true
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-90",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "函数调用",
      "body": "```elixir\nmodule_name.function_name(arg1, arg2)\n```\n\n示例：\n\n```elixir\nEnum.map([1, 2, 3], &(&1 * 2))\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-93",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%E9%BB%98%E8%AE%A4%E5%80%BC",
      "body": "%60%60%60elixir%0Adef%20function_name(parameter%20%5C%5C%20%E9%BB%98%E8%AE%A4%E5%80%BC)%20do%0A%20%20%23%20%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E4%BD%93%0Aend%0A%60%60%60%0A%0A%E7%A4%BA%E4%BE%8B%EF%BC%9A%0A%0A%60%60%60elixir%0Adef%20greet(name%20%5C%5C%20%22World%22)%20do%0A%20%20%22Hello%2C%20%23%7Bname%7D!%22%0Aend%0A%60%60%60",
      "encoded": true
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-96",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "可变参数数量",
      "body": "```elixir\ndef function_name(param1, param2 \\\\ []) do\n  # 函数体\nend\n```\n\n示例：\n\n```elixir\ndef sum(numbers) do\n  Enum.sum(numbers)\nend\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-99",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E6%96%87%E6%A1%A3%E6%B3%A8%E9%87%8A",
      "body": "%60%60%60elixir%0A%40doc%20%22%22%22%0A%E8%BF%99%E6%98%AF%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E7%9A%84%E6%96%87%E6%A1%A3%E3%80%82%0A%22%22%22%0A%60%60%60%0A%0A%E7%A4%BA%E4%BE%8B%EF%BC%9A%0A%0A%60%60%60elixir%0A%40doc%20%22%22%22%0AAdds%20two%20numbers%20together.%0A%0A%23%23%20%E7%A4%BA%E4%BE%8B%0A%0A%20%20%20%20iex%3E%20MyModule.add(1%2C%202)%0A%20%20%20%203%0A%22%22%22%0Adef%20add(a%2C%20b)%20do%0A%20%20a%20%2B%20b%0Aend%0A%60%60%60%0A%0A%E8%BF%99%E4%BA%9B%E6%98%AF%20Elixir%20%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E8%A6%81%E7%82%B9%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%B8%AE%E5%8A%A9%E4%BD%A0%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E7%BC%96%E5%86%99%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E3%80%82",
      "encoded": true
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-103",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "匿名函数",
      "body": "```elixir\niex> sum = fn (a, b) -> a + b end\niex> sum.(2, 3)\n5\n```\n\n可以使用 & 语法来简化匿名函数的定义：\n\n```elixir\niex> sum = &(&1 + &2)\niex> sum.(2, 3)\n5\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-106",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "闭包",
      "body": "匿名函数去引用外部的变量，这通常被称为闭包。\n\n```elixir\niex> double = fn a -> add.(a, a) end\n#Function<6.71889879/1 in :erl_eval.expr/5>\ndouble.(2)\n4\n```\n\n闭包与守卫\n\n```elixir\niex> f = fn\n  x, y when x > 0 -> x + y\n  x, y -> x * y\nend\n\niex> f.(1, 3)\n4\niex> f.(-1, 3)\n-3\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-110",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "%E5%91%BD%E5%90%8D%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0",
      "body": "%E5%91%BD%E5%90%8D%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E6%98%AF%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%20def%20%E5%85%B3%E9%94%AE%E5%AD%97%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E5%9C%A8%E6%9F%90%E4%B8%AA%E6%A8%A1%E5%9D%97%E4%B8%AD%0A%0A%60%60%60elixir%0Adefmodule%20Greeter%20do%0A%20%20def%20hello(name)%20do%0A%20%20%20%20%22Hello%2C%20%22%20%3C%3E%20name%0A%20%20end%0Aend%0A%0Aiex%3E%20Greeter.hello(%22Sean%22)%0A%22Hello%2C%20Sean%22%0A%60%60%60%0A%0A%E7%AE%80%E5%86%99%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%80%E8%A1%8C%EF%BC%9A%0A%0A%60%60%60elixir%0Adefmodule%20Greeter%20do%0A%20%20def%20hello(name)%2C%20do%3A%20%22Hello%2C%20%22%20%3C%3E%20name%0Aend%0A%60%60%60%0A%0A%E7%A7%81%E6%9C%89%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%0A%0A%60%60%60elixir%0Adefmodule%20Greeter%20do%0A%20%20def%20hello(name)%2C%20do%3A%20phrase%20%3C%3E%20name%0A%20%20%23%20%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8defp%E6%9D%A5%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E7%A7%81%E6%9C%89%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%0A%20%20defp%20phrase%2C%20do%3A%20%22Hello%2C%20%22%20%0Aend%0A%60%60%60%0A%0A%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E7%9A%84%E9%BB%98%E8%AE%A4%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%EF%BC%9A%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%20%60%5C%5C%60%20%E6%9D%A5%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E9%BB%98%E8%AE%A4%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%0A%0A%60%60%60elixir%0Adefmodule%20Greeter%20do%0A%20%20def%20hello(name%2C%20language_code%20%5C%5C%20%22en%22)%20do%0A%20%20%20%20phrase(language_code)%20%3C%3E%20name%0A%20%20end%0A%0A%20%20defp%20phrase(%22en%22)%2C%20do%3A%20%22Hello%2C%20%22%0A%20%20defp%20phrase(%22es%22)%2C%20do%3A%20%22Hola%2C%20%22%0Aend%0A%60%60%60",
      "encoded": true
    },
    {
      "id": "s6-118",
      "sectionId": "s6",
      "title": "Enumerables 与 Streams",
      "body": ">\n> Elixir 提供了 Enum 和 Stream 两个模块，用于处理集合。\n>"
    },
    {
      "id": "s6-119",
      "sectionId": "s6",
      "title": "Enum",
      "body": ">\n> Enum 模块提供了对集合的常用操作，如 map、filter、reduce、sort、chunk、join、into 等。\n\n```elixir\niex> Enum.map([1, 2, 3], fn x -> x * 2 end)\n[2, 4, 6]\niex> Enum.map(%{1 => 2, 3 => 4}, fn {k, v} -> k * v end)\n[2, 12]\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "s6-121",
      "sectionId": "s6",
      "title": "Stream",
      "body": "%3E%0A%3E%20%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%BAEnum%E7%9A%84%E6%9B%BF%E4%BB%A3%E5%93%81%EF%BC%8CElixir%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E4%BA%86%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E6%87%92%E6%83%B0%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%E7%9A%84Stream%E6%A8%A1%E5%9D%97%0A%0A%60%60%60elixir%0Aiex%3E%201..100_000%20%7C%3E%20Stream.map(%26(%261%20*%203))%20%7C%3E%20Stream.filter(odd%3F)%20%7C%3E%20Enum.sum()%0A7500000000%0A%60%60%60%0A%0A%3E%20%E6%B5%81%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%0A%0A%60%60%60elixir%0Aiex%3E%20stream%20%3D%20File.stream!(%22path%2Fto%2Ffile%22)%0A%25File.Stream%7B%0A%20%20line_or_bytes%3A%20%3Aline%2C%0A%20%20modes%3A%20%5B%3Araw%2C%20%3Aread_ahead%2C%20%3Abinary%5D%2C%0A%20%20path%3A%20%22path%2Fto%2Ffile%22%2C%0A%20%20raw%3A%20true%0A%7D%0AEnum.take(stream%2C%2010)%0A%0A%23%20%E4%B8%8A%E9%9D%A2%E7%9A%84%E4%BE%8B%E5%AD%90%E5%B0%86%E6%8F%90%E5%8F%96%E6%89%80%E9%80%89%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E7%9A%84%E5%89%8D10%E8%A1%8C%E3%80%82%E8%BF%99%E6%84%8F%E5%91%B3%E7%9D%80%E6%B5%81%E5%AF%B9%E4%BA%8E%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7%E5%9E%8B%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E7%94%9A%E8%87%B3%E6%98%AF%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90%E7%AD%89%E6%85%A2%E9%80%9F%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90%E9%9D%9E%E5%B8%B8%E6%9C%89%E7%94%A8%E3%80%82%0A%60%60%60",
      "encoded": true
    },
